title: Putting The Final Touches On Emacs - Configuring Emacs 07
description:
On this 7th (and possibly final) episode in the Configuring Emacs series, I cover a ton of new programs and final tweaks of the config file, including: electric pair mode, git timemachine, magit, perspective, rainbow delimiters, tldr, and more.
